content.p: The Institute of Work, Organisation and Wellbeing is an international centre of excellence for study and research in applied psychology. The Institute of Work, Organisation and Wellbeing is: Our international team has a pool of highly qualified staff who are active in teaching and research with areas of expertise including occupational psychology, health psychology, clinical psychology and social psychology.
